#: ../../user-manual/administer/settings.rst:2893
msgid ""
"This setting controls how many immediate :term:`child <child record>` "
"descriptions are loaded below the top-level description when users first "
"visit a hierarchical description's :term:`view page`. It also controls the "
"number of top-level descriptions that are added to the :term:`hierarchy "
"browser` on first load"
