"この設定は、ユーザーが階層的な記述の:term:`ビューページ`を初めて訪れたときに、トップレベルの記述の下に読み込まれる直下の:term:`子<child"
" record>`記述の数を制御します。また、初回読み込み時に:term:`階層ブラウザ`に追加されるトップレベルの記述の数も制御します。"

#: ../../user-manual/administer/settings.rst:2899
msgid ""
"Like the sidebar treeview, for performance reasons AtoM may not load all "
"available descriptions at once in the full-width treeview, when there are "
"many immediate :term:`children <child record>` below the top-level "
"description in the :term:`archival unit`. The default value for this "
"behavior is 50 - meaning, if there are more than 50 immediate children below"
" the parent description, AtoM will add a count of the number of remaining "
"records not immediately displayed to a button in the top right corner."
msgstr ""
